<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dieter II. Landschad von Steinach, Viztum zu Aschaffenburg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Göldlein, Diener der Stadt, wegen der Juden Josef und Mose Pützel an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="103r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_208_r1l11"><expan>Dıeth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lantſchad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_208_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> als Jr vns nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von yoſep pücʒels </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l13">des Juden vnd Moſſe ſeins ſuns <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc Alſo <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> wır ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l14"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> / Dem wır befolhen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l15"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . mıt eẅ <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu reden / Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> / VVas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l16"><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l17"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> . Daʒ Jr Jm das <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l18">gütlıch von vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> vnd <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan> wellet / als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l19">Denn wo wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meıncʒ <expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l20"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l21"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> Andree <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="103r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Dieth<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lantschad<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Yosep Püczels des juden
                        und Mosse seins suns <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., also
                                <expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und das gütlich von uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> und <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wellet. Als etc. Denn wo wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz <expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Andree
                        <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
